### Shopping Cart Tests
### Test cart operations (add, update, remove items)

@token = {{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}
@productId = {{createProduct.response.body.id}}
@productId2 = {{createProduct2.response.body.id}}

### 1. Get Current Cart (Empty)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/cart?userId=user-123

### 2. Add Item to Cart
# @name addToCart
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 3. Add Second Item
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId2}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 4. Get Cart with Items
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/cart?userId=user-123

### 5. Update Item Quantity (Increase)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 3
}

### 6. Update Item Quantity (Decrease to 0 = Remove)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId2}}",
  "quantity": 0
}

### 7. Remove Item from Cart
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}"
}

### 8. Clear Entire Cart
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/cart?userId=user-123

### 9. Add Items Again (for order test)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 10. Transfer Cart from Session to User (after login)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/cart/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "guest-session-123"
}